775
00:40:02,428 --> 00:40:03,268
Huaijin.

776
00:40:03,948 --> 00:40:04,868
I broke my promise.

777
00:40:06,268 --> 00:40:07,108
Sorry.

778
00:40:09,428 --> 00:40:11,147
