797
00:41:16,468 --> 00:41:17,308
Yeah.

798
00:41:17,507 --> 00:41:18,347
No misunderstandings.

799
00:41:19,107 --> 00:41:19,947
In the end,

800
00:41:20,827 --> 00:41:21,667
